==English==

===Transitive verb===
'''to quantize'''
#{{physics}} to [[limit]] the [[number]] of [[possible]] [[value]]s of a [[quantity]], or [[state]]s of a [[system]], by applying the [[rule]]s of [[quantum mechanics]]
#(''telecoms'') to [[approximate]] a [[continuously]] [[varying]] [[signal]] by one whose [[amplitude]] can only have a [[set]] of [[discrete]] values

